This is the protocol for a review and there is no abstract. The objectives are as follows:, The aim of the review is to assess the effectiveness of non hormonal therapies for improving hot flushes in patients with breast cancer., Primary Objective:, To examine the effectiveness of non-hormonal treatments for relieving hot flushes in women with breast cancer compared to placebo or no treatment group., Secondary Objectives:, To determine adverse effects of non-hormonal treatments, To evaluate the impact on quality of life of non-hormonal treatments versus control or placebo